  ('generalpolice-3218f787-moex-00288', 'generalpolice-3218f787', 'generalpolice-3218f787-moex-111-696aa37c', 'sub-generalpolice-3218f787-07', NULL, 'essay', '童年逆境經驗（AdverseChildhoodExperiences，ACEs）研究發現，具有
