  ('generalpolice-3218f787-moex-00289', 'generalpolice-3218f787', 'generalpolice-3218f787-moex-111-696aa37c', 'sub-generalpolice-3218f787-07', NULL, 'essay', '在帶領諮商團體時，帶領者能「催化此時此地並進行闡釋」，是帶領者相
